    Title: I Ching
  Title: The Man of Many Qualities
Title: Acquiring Experience
---
The man guards against the loss of his individuality. He should not imitate
persons of senior rank or act like a flippant girl throwing herself at a
handsome man. Neither should he accept overtures from such subordinates.
